      "author": "Quorafind",
      "description": "## What's New in 0.5.0\n\n### New Features\n- Replace verification system with PKMer OAuth login (register at [pkmer.cn](https://pkmer.cn))\n- Custom grid system (TemplifyGrid) replacing react-grid-layout\n- Local widget types: clocks, calendars, todos, pomodoro, countdown, habit tracker, etc.\n- Dataview widget type for rendering Dataview queries in layouts\n- Base widget type for generic embedded content\n- Background customization: patterns, images, and videos with opacity/blur/size controls\n- Banner (cover image) support with repositioning\n- Page icon support (icons and emoji)\n\n### Improvements\n- Migrate to Tailwind CSS v4 with improved build performance\n- Improved document sync logic and conflict resolution\n- Better overall rendering performance\n- Updated translations (English and Chinese)\n\n### Fixes\n- Kanban compatibility issue\n- Widget rendering issues",
